subject: Dear Christopher
body: Monday Lottery Board Inigo Business Centres, Blackwell House, Guildhall Yard London EC2V 5AE, United Kingdom. In other to elaborate further, I suggest you provide us with your winning reference number so that we can provide adequate answers to your questions.  I think this question should be channeled directly to Precision Logistics and Diplomatic Delivery Services, however, kindly provide your winning reference number for record purposes and you will be supplied with the desirable answers you seek. Regards Mr. Alexander Fred Prize Remittance Director.
